{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468406778,"sessionID":"ses_1eb0996a3ffe3q2wq6MLoHhiQh","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:22","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","content":"Hi,\n\nAll requested updates to GO:0102177 have been made and are committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nSummary of changes:\n- Name updated to '4alpha-monomethylsterol monooxygenase activity' to match EC:1.14.18.11\n- Definition and reaction updated to the full RHEA:58868 reaction\n- RHEA xref updated to RHEA:58868 (exactMatch)\n- MetaCyc xref updated to MetaCyc:RXN-19724\n- Parent changed from GO:0016709 to GO:0016716 (EC:1.14.18.-)\n- Removed GOC:pz from definition references\n\nThanks for the detailed report and checklist — it made the edits very straightforward.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778468406770,"end":1778468406777}},"id":"prt_e14fa3fc2001NRAxWTf7TvbWqH","sessionID":"ses_1eb0996a3ffe3q2wq6MLoHhiQh","messageID":"msg_e14fa3ac8001Djhg27LocViNM3"}}
